steps.name: Given I am login on staging env
Then I should see Mobile screen display
When I select tab name Pages with index 1
When I delete screen with name JIT012 and verify
When I add new screen with name JIT012
Then I should see the screen with name JIT012 display in list Pages
When I navigate to menu "Mobile app" with submenu "Navigation"
When I wait Mobile Navigation screen display
When I reset the navigation tree
When I add item navigation type "Stack Navigation" to stack root "Navigation Container" with index 1
When I add item navigation type JIT012 to stack root "Stack Navigation" with index 1
Then I should see item JIT012 index 1 display in navigation tree
When I select item navigation name JIT012 with index 1
Then I should see property infos of navigation display
Then I should see general textbox with NAME "key" has value JIT012
When I reset the navigation tree
Then I should not see item JIT012 index 1 display in navigation tree
Then I should not see property infos of navigation display
When I navigate to menu "Mobile app" with submenu "Mobile Editor"
